Give it here!

281
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:29,128
- You ain't got no apple, huh?
- No!

282
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:31,481
Let me tell you something.
This is my street.

283
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:34,126
