it's really for my father.

372
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,608
I see.

373
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:03,768
- For Donald Miller?
- Yeah.

374
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,450
I know it sounds complicated...

375
00:28:05,560 --> 00:28:08,643
