00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:48,842
I'll keep an eye out for you.

418
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:51,008
Thanks.

419
00:31:51,120 --> 00:31:53,646
- Good-bye, Aaron.
- Good-bye.

